<td valign="top">
<p>We all use software in our everyday working lives, for emails, word processing, spreadsheets and the like, yet the vast majority of SME’s personnel records are in paper format, with the odd spreadsheet for good measure.</p>
<p>Tremendous advances have been made in software technology over recent years, and now personnel software is flexible, easy to use and a powerful reporting tool.</p>
<p>Modern software packages range from stand alone 1 PC packages, to fully integrated systems capable of dealing with people issues on a global basis even for SME’s. Talk to us and let us guide you through a range of different solutions.</p></td>
